headline: Regency Centers Invites You to Join Its Fourth Quarter 2024 Earnings Conference Call
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., Jan. 06, 2025 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- Regency Centers Corporation (“Regency Centers” or the “Company”) (NASDAQ: REG) will announce its fourth quarter 2024 earnings results on Thursday, February 6, 2025, after the market closes.
